OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780168284
OL,3,CTwo people killed and three seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in crash
OL,6,FTwo people have died and three more
OL,7,Fwere seriously injured in a crash in
OL,8,FNorthumberland.
OL,10,FTwo cars were involved in the
OL,11,Fcollision on the A1 just before 4am on
OL,12,FSaturday (30 May).
OL,14,FIt happened at the junction for
OL,15,FWandylaw, north of Alnwick.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
