PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780168284
OL,3,CTwo people killed and three seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in crash
OL,6,FIt was reported that a silver Nissan
OL,7,FJuke car was travelling southbound
OL,8,Fwhen, for reasons yet to be
OL,9,Festablished, it collided with a blue
OL,10,FVauxhall Corsa car travelling in the
OL,11,Fopposite direction.
OL,13,FThe drivers of both vehicles - a woman
OL,14,Fin her 50s from the Juke and a man in
OL,15,Fhis 40s from the Corsa - died at the
OL,16,Fscene.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
