FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780168284
OL,3,CTwo people killed and three seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in crash
OL,6,FTwo passengers in the Juke - a woman
OL,7,Fin her 20s and a secondary-school aged
OL,8,Fboy ` along with a female passenger
OL,9,Ffrom the Corsa in her 20s, were all
OL,10,Ftaken to hospital with serious
OL,11,Finjuries.
OL,13,FThe next of kin of the occupants from
OL,14,Fboth vehicles have been informed and
OL,15,Fthey are receiving support from
OL,16,Fspecialist officers.
OL,18,FA section of the A1 in both directions
OL,19,Fbetween Ellingham and Purdy Lodge was
OL,20,Fclosed for about ten hours, but the
OL,21,Froad has since reopened.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
