FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780168284
OL,3,CTwo people killed and three seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in crash
OL,6,FOfficers from Northumbria Police's
OL,7,FRoads Policing Unit have appealed for
OL,8,Fwitnesses to come forward. They are
OL,9,Fespecially keen to hear from anyone
OL,10,Fwith CCTV or dashcam footage of the
OL,11,Fmoments leading up to the collision.
OL,13,FSergeant Alex Partington, of
OL,14,FNorthumbria Police, said: "This is a
OL,15,Fdevastating incident where two people
OL,16,Fhave tragically lost their lives while
OL,17,Fthree others remain in a serious
OL,18,Fcondition.
OL,26,@vD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780168284
OL,3,CTwo people killed and three seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in crash
OL,6,F"I would like to express my heartfelt
OL,7,Fcondolences to the loved ones of all
OL,8,Faffected at this incredibly difficult
OL,9,Ftime, and we will continue to support
OL,10,Fthem in any way we can."
OL,12,FSgt Partington added: "Our
OL,13,Finvestigation to establish the exact
OL,14,Fcircumstances leading to this
OL,15,Fcollision is now under way, and we are
OL,16,Falready conducting a range of
OL,17,Fenquiries.
OL,19,F"We are now appealing to any motorists
OL,20,For witnesses who were travelling in
OL,21,Fthe area at this time to come forward.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]tD@WOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
