PN,42106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780168284
OL,3,CTwo people killed and three seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in crash
OL,6,F"We are particularly keen to hear from
OL,7,Fthose who have dashcam footage which
OL,8,Fmay have captured the collision or
OL,9,Fthis section of road in the moments
OL,10,Fleading to it.
OL,12,F"No matter how insignificant your
OL,13,Finformation may seem, it could prove
OL,14,Fvital to our investigation and help
OL,15,Fprovide answers to the loved ones of
OL,16,Fall affected."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@NO]
