OL,3,CTwo people killed and three seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in crash
OL,6,FAnyone with information or footage
OL,7,Fshould get in touch by sending
OL,8,FNorthumbria Police a direct message on
OL,9,Fsocial media, or by using live chat
OL,10,Fand report forms on the force's
OL,11,Fwebsite. Those unable to make contact
OL,12,Fin these ways can call 101.
OL,14,FThe police reference number is NP-
OL,15,F20260530-0159.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
